sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant FE as Frontend (React/JS)
    participant BE as Backend (Hono)
    participant DB as Database (Firestore)

    Note over FE,BE: API Request (HTTP POST)
    FE->>+BE: POST /api/votes { boothId: "B-123" }
    
    Note right of BE: Logic: Validation & Storage
    BE->>DB: Write Data
    DB-->>BE: Success
    
    Note over BE,FE: API Response (JSON)
    BE-->>-FE: 200 OK { votes: 50, message: "完了" }
    
    Note left of FE: Update UI with Response Data
